# Daily SunTimes Update
# Automated daily content refresh

Update today's sunrise/sunset data for all locations.

Tasks:
1. Calculate current date sunrise/sunset times for all tracked cities
2. Update "today" pages with fresh data
3. Generate new blog posts if significant events (solstices, equinoxes)
4. Update social media content suggestions
5. Refresh sitemap with any new content
6. Validate all generated HTML and fix any issues

Use real-time solar calculation APIs and update the following:
- public/locations/*/today.html
- src/data/current-times.json
- public/sitemap.xml

Ensure all times are accurate and properly formatted.